metadata.name: room3
metadata.description:
A room to commemorate endless summer evenings spent by the ocean. 
The warm, salty breeze fills you with the exact feeling you experienced the first time you smelled it as a child. The air is rich with the song of the cicadas and a pleasant moisture that wraps around your "body" like a thin but warm blanket. This is a beta version of course and your experience will improve over time. As for the glitch: after a few hours of glaring at the eternally setting sun, you won't even notice it anymore.
